thumb.title: Eastside Weight Loss
thumb.description: Eastside Weight Loss Clinic specializes in Kirkland weight loss, offering a personalized, doctor-supervised program focused on healthy eating, metabolic resetting, and inflammation reduction. Led by Dr. Ryan Coogan D.C., the clinic provides tailored plans, natural supplements, and continuous support to help clients achieve sustainable weight loss. With in-office and virtual coaching, Eastside Weight Loss Clinic ensures flexibility and long-term success.
